Professors Receive Honor from American Welding Society (Professors Daryush K. Aidun, Daniel T. Valentine, Alumnus Dr. Alireza Bahrami '14) received the MaKay-Helm Award for their research paper "Interaction of Gravity Forces in Spot GTA Weld Pool," which was part of Dr. Bahrami's PhD. Thesis. http://www.clarkson.edu/news/photos/aws-award.jpg
